<lb ed="C I" n="0207a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>陳榮等三百餘人造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0207a01"/><p id="pI01p0207a0101">□薩主杜僧達為亡過見存　化生主李石</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b01"/><p id="pI01p0207b0101">□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">齊</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">河</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">清</unclear>二年歲次癸未十一月辛酉朔廿三日癸未
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b02"/>□□□□湛。非視聽所監。妙理虛沖。豈思慮<note n="0207001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31169;＝能【史】</note><app n="0207001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">能</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31169;</rdg></app>究。自不行<note n="0207002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30997;＝備【史】</note><app n="0207002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">備</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30997;</rdg></app>果<note n="0207003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31005;＝員【史】</note><app n="0207003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">員</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31005;</rdg></app>。達觀&CB07099;<note n="0207004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01002;＝礙【史】</note><app n="0207004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">礙</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01002;</rdg></app>。寧<app source="0207001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">能</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31169;</rdg></app>出沒自由。沉浮
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b03"/>□□□□如來<note n="0207005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30562;＝權【史】</note><app n="0207005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30562;</rdg></app>應三<note n="0207006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30998;＝界【史】</note><app n="0207006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">界</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30998;</rdg></app>。為群盲開輝。息耀潛光。現神奇之變。慈波浩汗。澆潤無<note n="0207007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30999;＝邊【史】</note><app n="0207007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30999;</rdg></app>。澤<note n="0207008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31003;＝流【史】</note><app n="0207008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">流</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31003;</rdg></app>万劫。寤
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b04"/>□□□□□義主陳榮。李潘等。慧解玄宗。心照法相。率諸法義三百餘人。傾資竭賄。敬造石像一
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b05"/>□□□□□下及蒼生。工盡世奇。斤庛謝<note n="0207009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31000;＝巧【史】</note><app n="0207009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">巧</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31000;</rdg></app>。圖丹約<note n="0207010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31004;＝彩【史】</note><app n="0207010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彩</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31004;</rdg></app>。<note n="0207011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">鎣＝瑩【史】</note><app n="0207011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瑩</lem><rdg wit="【原】">鎣</rdg></app>精麗日。但聖<note n="0207012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30518;＝顏【史】</note><app n="0207012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顏</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30518;</rdg></app>殊特。彫刻難比。且傳經
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b06"/>□□□□□□其詞曰。　　眇眇神姿。攸攸聖跡。含識悲悼。嗚呼<note n="0207013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30415;＝痛【史】</note><app n="0207013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">痛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30415;</rdg></app>惜。夜<note n="0207014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07656;＝喪【史】</note><app n="0207014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07656;</rdg></app>寶珠。橫執<note n="0207015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31001;＝瓦【史】</note><app n="0207015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瓦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31001;</rdg></app>礫。水不
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b07"/>□□□□□□□□□求。圖金鐫石。彫瑍現想。光色輝怡。神<note n="0207016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00370;＝虯【史】</note><app n="0207016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00370;</rdg></app>負足。吐萼承基。雙菩立侍。方丈不
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b08"/>□□□□□□□□□□塔乘空。諸天<note n="0207017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31002;＝斜【史】</note><app n="0207017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">斜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31002;</rdg></app>飛。撫琴<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">奏</unclear>□。□□有徽。福鍾帝主。延祚千零。干戈息刃。
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b09"/>□□□□□□□□□□□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">須</unclear>捨。花蔭菩提。□□□□□□□□□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b10"/>□□□□□□　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　維那朱　興　維那郝僧憐
<lb ed="C I" n="0207b11"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　□□□□貴　維那陳廣達</p>
